<p>If you think youâ€™ve found a bug in the Leap Day theme, please <a href="https://github.com/pages-themes/leap-day/issues">check the existing issues</a>, and if no one has reported the problem, <a href="https://github.com/pages-themes/leap-day/issues/new">open a new issue</a>.</p>

<p>If you have a general question about the theme, how to implement it, or how to customize it for your site you have two options:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Search for your query on <a href="https://support.github.com/?q=pages+Leap Day+theme"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">support.github.com</code></a>, which will also look for similar topics on <a href="https://github.community/search?q=pages+Leap Day+theme"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">github.community</code></a></li>
  <li>Ask your question of the Jekyll community on <a href="https://talk.jekyllrb.com/">talk.jekyllrb.com</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/contact?form%5Bsubject%5D=GitHub%20Pages%20theme%20pages-themes/leap-day">Contact GitHub Support</a></li>
